instance virtual_to_physical_interaction : DTDFVocab:VirtualToPhysical [
    base:desc "The Digital Twin sends control directives back to the PT through RabbitMQ. Commands to turn the heatbed and fan on/off, along with timing parameters (heating duration H and wait duration C), are issued by the DT and consumed by the controller running on the Pi, which in turn drives the MOSFET‑mediated actuators."
